===Magic===
Ruby jewellery can be enchanted using [[Lvl-3 Enchant]], requiring level 49 [[Magic]]. The spell requires 1 [[cosmic rune]], 5 [[fire rune]]s, and the piece of ruby [[jewellery]] that is to be enchanted.
